Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}UNCHAIN YOUR LIFE　魂引き裂いて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}UNBREAK DESTINY を切り開いて
